name: Pige
public_notice: Pige Inu (PINU) has rebranded to Pige (PIGE) and recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. For more information, please visit this post.

description.en:
Pige Inu is a community-driven meme cryptocurrency on Binance Smart Chain. Our contract is fully renounced, we have low tax on buys and sells.

At Pige Inu, we are exceptionally proud of the community that is being built surrounding our token. We work to provide engagement through our social media pages, as well as timely announcements, and transparency as the company develops.
